item.title: 【Singles (lossless)】FLAC - Billlie - 'The Billlie's Odditorium' The First Edition
item.description:
"'The Billlie's Odditorium' The First Edition" (stylized as "'the Billlie's odditorium' the first edition") is the third digital single by Billlie. It was released on November 27, 2023 with "The Soul Savior ~ I Don't Need a Superman" serving as the single's title track.



Track list
